                 <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Uḷḷamuṭaiyāṉ Cūṭāmaṇi</title>, also known as <title xml:lang="ta">Cūṭāmaṇi Uḷḷamuṭaiyāṉ</title> and <title xml:lang="ta"> Uḷḷamuṭaiyāṉ</title>, is a work on astrology by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author" key="Uḷḷamuṭaiyāṉ">Uḷḷamuṭaiyāṉ</persName> (possibly 12th or 13th century according to Zvelebil 1995, p. 720). It is not to be confused with the homonym work by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author" key="Maṇṭalapuruṭar">Maṇṭalapuruṭaṉ</persName>. See Sweetman (2012, p. 95).</p>
<p>The work (<foreign xml:lang="ta">mūlam</foreign> only) is apparently incomplete.</p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (July 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> </summary>
                  
